data.description: Looking for a maintenance free home, Located in the highly desirable 55+ community of Britton Falls, this one bedroom home w/ additional "flex room" has been extremely well maintained. The stand-out features included: spacious kitchen w/oversized island, ample closet/storage throughout the home and in garage, convenient main level laundry and a community that you will enjoy for years to come. The amenities w/in the neighborhood include walking trails, pool, tennis/pickleball courts and lots of event space. If you're seeking a home in a community that keeps you connected and active, then look no further.
